WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:33.280 --> 00:00:40.090
I bow to all the seekers of Truth.

00:00:40.090 --> 00:00:54.350
When we are seeking the Truth we have to know
we have to be honest about it.

00:00:54.350 --> 00:00:58.500
Because it is benevolent for us, not for others.

00:00:58.500 --> 00:01:05.199
We are seeking the Truth for ourselves, not
for others.

00:01:05.199 --> 00:01:14.539
The another thing we have to remember, very
humbly, that truth is what it is.

00:01:14.539 --> 00:01:21.280
We can not change it, we can not organize
it, we can not maneuver it.

00:01:21.280 --> 00:01:26.490
It is what has been and will be.

00:01:26.490 --> 00:01:30.990
And what is the Truth?

00:01:30.990 --> 00:01:36.479
The truth is that you are the Spirit.

00:01:36.479 --> 00:01:46.790
You are not this body, you are not this mind,
you are not this ego, and you are not this

00:01:46.790 --> 00:01:47.930
conditioning.

00:01:47.930 --> 00:01:49.829
You are the Spirit.

00:01:49.829 --> 00:01:55.500
But so far you have been a humane being.

00:01:55.500 --> 00:02:04.840
But to be humane being itself is a very great
thing.

00:02:04.840 --> 00:02:08.869
Is the greatest thing – to be a humane being.

00:02:08.869 --> 00:02:18.299
Perhaps we have not realized the value of
our life because we do not know what we are.

00:02:18.299 --> 00:02:31.540
The way we waste our time, waste our energies,
waste our attention on things, which are senseless,

00:02:31.540 --> 00:02:40.370
because we still have to understand the greatness
of our being.

00:02:40.370 --> 00:02:52.680
Humane beings are made with such care, so
beautifully, such delicate working of the

00:02:52.680 --> 00:02:59.430
Divine from ameba to this stage passing through
various stages, such a beautiful thing has

00:02:59.430 --> 00:03:03.209
been created as a humane being.

00:03:03.209 --> 00:03:09.849
But first we must have this attention to our
Self that there must be something.

00:03:09.849 --> 00:03:18.459
It can not be a purposelessly [WAY or DOING],
it can not be something just a chance.

00:03:18.459 --> 00:03:21.780
Is a wrong idea to play with.

00:03:21.780 --> 00:03:36.200
If the gravitation force of the Earth or anyone
of the galaxies changes, then be disaster,

00:03:36.200 --> 00:03:38.870
absolute disaster.

00:03:38.870 --> 00:03:44.450
So many things in the cosmos, if you study,
the coefficients that works out, the different

00:03:44.450 --> 00:03:51.870
balancing and the different weights and the
movements of the different bodies show us

00:03:51.870 --> 00:03:53.549
that there must be some purpose.

00:03:53.549 --> 00:04:03.450
And they do not trouble us; it’s all as
if made for the stage for humane beings.

00:04:03.450 --> 00:04:07.379
That the humane beings have to come on the
stage and all the preparation is made for

00:04:07.379 --> 00:04:11.170
the great drama.

00:04:11.170 --> 00:04:17.739
I think it’s high time that great scientists
should look at it and start wondering why

00:04:17.739 --> 00:04:20.880
is it the way it is made.

00:04:20.880 --> 00:04:25.950
Why we are so much looked after.

00:04:25.950 --> 00:04:34.960
The whole cosmos seems to be within ourselves
as if we have buttons, which move the cosmos,

00:04:34.960 --> 00:04:39.469
which control the cosmos.

00:04:39.469 --> 00:04:46.690
Everything is going on so smoothly otherwise,
except when we do not try to understand ourselves.

00:04:46.690 --> 00:04:57.009
It has been said practically in all the Scriptures
that you have to seek your Self; you have

00:04:57.009 --> 00:04:59.170
to find your Self.

00:04:59.170 --> 00:05:09.530
Though I think many of this Scriptures have
been little bit changed and have been used

00:05:09.530 --> 00:05:17.030
for certain purposes, still they could not
get over this point that you have to become

00:05:17.030 --> 00:05:21.570
the Self, you have to be born again.

00:05:21.570 --> 00:05:24.950
But that is not an artificial thing.

00:05:24.950 --> 00:05:29.130
We are humane beings not artificially made.

00:05:29.130 --> 00:05:35.210
We are made really by some sort of a living
force from ameba.

00:05:35.210 --> 00:05:42.200
We are not just made with some sort of a thinking
or a mental projection.

00:05:42.200 --> 00:05:49.860
It is not a mental projection by which we
have been humane beings, it is something spontaneously

00:05:49.860 --> 00:05:56.530
happening, a living force within us, which
has brought us to this stage - with a purpose,

00:05:56.530 --> 00:05:58.440
with a meaning.

00:05:58.440 --> 00:06:05.650
And now at this stage we are free to do what
we like.

00:06:05.650 --> 00:06:10.810
Many people ask Me, “What was the need to
give this freedom to humane beings?”

00:06:10.810 --> 00:06:12.940
It was very necessary.

00:06:12.940 --> 00:06:20.479
If you have to have the ultimate freedom you
must know how to deal with it.

00:06:20.479 --> 00:06:21.940
You have to understand.

00:06:21.940 --> 00:06:26.000
Of course, humane beings have to make mistakes.

00:06:26.000 --> 00:06:28.290
To err is humane.

00:06:28.290 --> 00:06:39.110
And we have to understand that this trial
– error and trial and error business – has

00:06:39.110 --> 00:06:45.699
made us understand, also those who have not
understood must understand, that there must

00:06:45.699 --> 00:06:53.590
be a wiser or surer way to achieve that goal
of Self-Realization, of Self-knowledge.

00:06:53.590 --> 00:07:05.210
Self-knowledge we do not have, we must admit
very humbly, we have had no system by which

00:07:05.210 --> 00:07:06.990
we could know ourselves.

00:07:06.990 --> 00:07:11.500
But think of a computer that is a humane being
is.

00:07:11.500 --> 00:07:14.900
As soon as you see Me you know I am there.

00:07:14.900 --> 00:07:22.319
You don’t have to go for programming, you
don’t have to consult anything, you don’t

00:07:22.319 --> 00:07:30.230
have to use any kind of computer or some sort
of a complicated machinery, automatically,

00:07:30.230 --> 00:07:35.900
spontaneously in a split of a second you know
that I’m standing before you and talking

00:07:35.900 --> 00:07:36.900
to you.

00:07:36.900 --> 00:07:38.470
Such a computer we can not create.

00:07:38.470 --> 00:07:44.150
But the Divine has created such a great computer
and that is the humane being.

00:07:44.150 --> 00:07:50.169
And this humane being is the only one who
is going to achieve that higher state, which

00:07:50.169 --> 00:07:55.260
we call as the spiritual state of the Self.

00:07:55.260 --> 00:08:03.569
Because in the science they deal with the
tree, I should say, the outside, but they

00:08:03.569 --> 00:08:07.160
can not go into the roots.

00:08:07.160 --> 00:08:11.610
To go into the roots you have to become a
subtler being.

00:08:11.610 --> 00:08:15.419
Unless and until you become a subtler being
you can not go into your roots to find out

00:08:15.419 --> 00:08:17.730
what are your roots are.

00:08:17.730 --> 00:08:20.980
And that is what is Self-Realization.

00:08:20.980 --> 00:08:28.470
When you become subtler then only you can
go into your being and can find out what actually

00:08:28.470 --> 00:08:29.470
you are.

00:08:29.470 --> 00:08:38.240
Also to look after a tree, which has not know
its roots, is a very difficult thing.

00:08:38.240 --> 00:08:44.990
What happens is that when you do not know
your roots and you start growing, and growing,

00:08:44.990 --> 00:08:55.170
and growing you go very deep down into that
where you find that you have lost your way.

00:08:55.170 --> 00:08:56.470
Actually you are not going deeper.

00:08:56.470 --> 00:09:00.800
You are spreading outside more and more.

00:09:00.800 --> 00:09:05.370
And then once you start going to extremes
because of your freedom you lose your way.

00:09:05.370 --> 00:09:11.550
That’s how today everybody is saying, “A
shock is going to come”.

00:09:11.550 --> 00:09:14.650
You are all going to face a shock.

00:09:14.650 --> 00:09:17.680
This is going to happen, that is going to
happen.

00:09:17.680 --> 00:09:23.140
But actually it is absolutely in your hands
because the whole of the cosmos is within

00:09:23.140 --> 00:09:24.140
you.

00:09:24.140 --> 00:09:28.860
The cosmos is working under your control complete.

00:09:28.860 --> 00:09:32.679
It is absolutely looking after you.

00:09:32.679 --> 00:09:41.270
Every element is looking after you to preserve
you, to guide you, to take you to the right

00:09:41.270 --> 00:09:42.270
thinking.

00:09:42.270 --> 00:09:44.550
But in your freedom you have to achieve that.

00:09:44.550 --> 00:09:49.880
This is a very big condition and there where
we fail to understand.

00:09:49.880 --> 00:09:54.709
Even there are many who say, “There is nothing
like Divine” and, “There is nothing like

00:09:54.709 --> 00:09:56.939
God.”

00:09:56.939 --> 00:10:01.299
In Russia I’ve been and I’ve been to China
and all the communist countries and they are

00:10:01.299 --> 00:10:04.560
in a way partially justify it.

00:10:04.560 --> 00:10:12.080
Because what they found, those people who
talk of God, those who say that, “We believe

00:10:12.080 --> 00:10:19.880
in God” and those who say that, “We believe
in religion”, can be irreligious.

00:10:19.880 --> 00:10:25.790
Anybody who can call himself a Christian,
Hindu, Muslim, say, Farsi, anything, is capable

00:10:25.790 --> 00:10:27.110
of any sin.

00:10:27.110 --> 00:10:31.150
Whatever he wants to do he can do it.

00:10:31.150 --> 00:10:37.300
Nobody can say that, “Because he was a Christian
he could not do it”.

00:10:37.300 --> 00:10:46.540
So the whole concept of religion becomes a
mental projection again an artificial thing.

00:10:46.540 --> 00:10:56.640
But if a person is a Self-Realized person
he goes beyond that, beyond temptations, beyond

00:10:56.640 --> 00:11:00.240
any kind of domination of any habits.

00:11:00.240 --> 00:11:08.060
He becomes a very strong person, very powerful
person and extremely compassionate.

00:11:08.060 --> 00:11:12.690
His compassion is active.

00:11:12.690 --> 00:11:17.150
Is not a compassion that, “I’ll form a
charitable institution, which lends money

00:11:17.150 --> 00:11:21.120
to people”, is not like that.

00:11:21.120 --> 00:11:29.070
The being itself emits compassion and this
compassion acts, acts and works out.

00:11:29.070 --> 00:11:35.310
For example you become like a light which
gives light to people and to yourself.

00:11:35.310 --> 00:11:37.160
You know others and you know yourself.

00:11:37.160 --> 00:11:43.120
That is the light of the Truth and unless
and until that happens one should not say

00:11:43.120 --> 00:11:51.100
that, “I’m a Self-Realized soul” or,
“I am a twice born” – is artificial.

00:11:51.100 --> 00:11:58.360
So what you have to understand that we are
living in a relative world.

00:11:58.360 --> 00:12:01.440
We talk relatively.

00:12:01.440 --> 00:12:07.500
We have to be in the absolute world, where
the Truth is absolute.

00:12:07.500 --> 00:12:13.329
There now before you I’m standing, you know
very well that I’m wearing a sari, which

00:12:13.329 --> 00:12:14.559
is white.

00:12:14.559 --> 00:12:20.390
But it’s a relative still because somebody
will say, “Oh, maybe it’s white”.

00:12:20.390 --> 00:12:24.930
Somebody will say, “It’s of white”,
somebody will say like that.

00:12:24.930 --> 00:12:35.179
Still you know something, but to know it absolutely,
meticulously the right thing, you have to

00:12:35.179 --> 00:12:36.179
be the Spirit.

00:12:36.179 --> 00:12:41.880
But what you know is much more than these
eyes can see or this nose can smell.

00:12:41.880 --> 00:12:50.870
Is much more, much more explicit, much more
clear cut.

00:12:50.870 --> 00:12:53.780
Like a person who is suffering, say, from
some disease.

00:12:53.780 --> 00:13:02.110
A child is suffering from some disease and
they don’t know what the disease is.

00:13:02.110 --> 00:13:09.360
So they have to go many various kinds of tests
and for that the gentlemen, the father, or

00:13:09.360 --> 00:13:12.190
the mother, they have to pay a lot of money.

00:13:12.190 --> 00:13:15.800
They go on finding about the child, what’s
wrong, what’s wrong, what’s wrong.

00:13:15.800 --> 00:13:18.010
They can not find it, what’s wrong with
the child.

00:13:18.010 --> 00:13:23.870
And they are so upset about it and within
three days a child dies and still the diagnoses

00:13:23.870 --> 00:13:24.870
is not coming.

00:13:24.870 --> 00:13:28.910
Is a very common thing.

00:13:28.910 --> 00:13:35.300
But when you are a Self-Realized soul you
can know what’s wrong with the child, exactly

00:13:35.300 --> 00:13:43.270
you can put down your finger on the problem
that he has.

00:13:43.270 --> 00:13:44.270
Now how does it happen?

00:13:44.270 --> 00:13:49.270
Here is already told you about the charkas
that we have, the centers within us.

00:13:49.270 --> 00:13:56.610
These are the centers, which on one side control
the cosmos, on the other side control us,

00:13:56.610 --> 00:14:02.390
give knowledge and on the other side they
give us the knowledge about others.

00:14:02.390 --> 00:14:03.790
These centers are within us.

00:14:03.790 --> 00:14:10.059
Now when I’m telling you all this you have
to have an open mind of a scientist.

00:14:10.059 --> 00:14:14.640
We shouldn’t just deny it because in your
concept it doesn’t fitting.

00:14:14.640 --> 00:14:21.430
But like a scientist please see to it that
if it is proved you have to accept that this

00:14:21.430 --> 00:14:23.360
is so.

00:14:23.360 --> 00:14:29.650
Now these charkas are within you, these centers
are within you, and these centers communicate

00:14:29.650 --> 00:14:36.939
to you through your fingertips what’s the
matter with a child.

00:14:36.939 --> 00:14:42.330
You can feel it on your fingertips, now five,
six, and seven centers, right side, seven

00:14:42.330 --> 00:14:43.330
centers.

00:14:43.330 --> 00:14:44.480
(Shri Mataji points to the chakra projections
on Her left and right palms.)

00:14:44.480 --> 00:14:48.610
The right side has got the seven centers,
if they are decoded properly and if you know

00:14:48.610 --> 00:14:52.930
what is the decoding is, putting the hand
towards a child, for a Realized soul it is

00:14:52.930 --> 00:14:54.300
very easy to see where is the problem.

00:14:54.300 --> 00:15:01.809
And as soon as he finds a problem and he knows
how to cure it he can cure people without

00:15:01.809 --> 00:15:02.809
going to doctors.

00:15:02.809 --> 00:15:09.260
Sahaja Yoga has cured, I must say, I don’t
want to claim it because I don’t want to

00:15:09.260 --> 00:15:12.880
open a hospital.

00:15:12.880 --> 00:15:16.680
We are here to create doctors and not patients.

00:15:16.680 --> 00:15:21.410
So even some patients who have come to us
have become doctors today in a way that they

00:15:21.410 --> 00:15:24.370
diagnose it on their fingertips.

00:15:24.370 --> 00:15:32.080
As Mohammed Sahib has clearly said that, “At
the time of your resurrection your hands will

00:15:32.080 --> 00:15:33.080
speak”.

00:15:33.080 --> 00:15:39.130
But still nobody wants to know about it, that’s
called as a resurrection time, as [SOUNDS

00:15:39.130 --> 00:15:41.130
LIKE – Kayama], nobody wants to talk about
it.

00:15:41.130 --> 00:15:46.400
“Your hands will speak and will give evidence
and witness against you”, clearly He has

00:15:46.400 --> 00:15:54.650
said it, I must say, He’d done such a lot
of work on the Self-knowledge; as Christ has

00:15:54.650 --> 00:15:58.230
also said so many things.

00:15:58.230 --> 00:16:01.240
But people don’t want to look at that side.

00:16:01.240 --> 00:16:09.910
Like to say that, “We must suffer” itself
is a nonsense, I think, how can you.

00:16:09.910 --> 00:16:17.189
Any God who is a compassionate Father would
like His children to suffer to meet Him?

00:16:17.189 --> 00:16:20.809
I mean, it doesn’t going to logic at all.

00:16:20.809 --> 00:16:25.500
But people accept this funny concept of sufferings.

00:16:25.500 --> 00:16:26.680
What about Christ?

00:16:26.680 --> 00:16:28.970
He suffered for us, isn’t it?

00:16:28.970 --> 00:16:32.690
Isn’t it that He suffered for us?

00:16:32.690 --> 00:16:38.050
If so, is has He left something for us to
be done, to be completed more than He has

00:16:38.050 --> 00:16:41.049
suffered?

00:16:41.049 --> 00:16:51.770
He has suffered for us and He has done the
job fully.

00:16:51.770 --> 00:16:58.440
We don’t have to do any more about it.

00:16:58.440 --> 00:17:01.660
He carried the cross.

00:17:01.660 --> 00:17:07.480
People make Him look like a TB patient, even
worse than that, just bones and the skins.

00:17:07.480 --> 00:17:14.290
It’s very surprising, how can you conceive
Christ like that?!

00:17:14.290 --> 00:17:23.699
Anyone of the people who say they are very
healthy people, let them carry the cross and

00:17:23.699 --> 00:17:25.419
we’ll see.

00:17:25.419 --> 00:17:34.679
It is so contradictory about Christ, there’s
surprisingly that He should say that you have

00:17:34.679 --> 00:17:38.000
to suffer.

00:17:38.000 --> 00:17:39.000
Same about Jews.

00:17:39.000 --> 00:17:46.300
I just don’t understand why should they
say that you have to suffer if their God is

00:17:46.300 --> 00:17:47.300
kind?

00:17:47.300 --> 00:17:55.020
Same about all other organized; all these
organized or perverted people who say that

00:17:55.020 --> 00:17:57.490
you have to suffer.

00:17:57.490 --> 00:18:01.200
Suddenly people become vegetarians, suddenly
they become fasting.

00:18:01.200 --> 00:18:05.700
In India though we have to fast in any case
because of lack of food, but they have fasting

00:18:05.700 --> 00:18:06.700
days.

00:18:06.700 --> 00:18:10.630
There are some people who fast at least five
days in a week.

00:18:10.630 --> 00:18:11.630
They fasting.

00:18:11.630 --> 00:18:12.630
What is the need to fast?

00:18:12.630 --> 00:18:14.670
If you ask for fasting you’ll have to fast
all your life.

00:18:14.670 --> 00:18:17.990
That’s what God gives you, “You fast now,
you want to fast?

00:18:17.990 --> 00:18:20.610
All right, have it fasting.”

00:18:20.610 --> 00:18:23.330
We are asking for trouble.

00:18:23.330 --> 00:18:24.740
You want to be miserable?

00:18:24.740 --> 00:18:27.760
All right, be miserable.

00:18:27.760 --> 00:18:28.810
You want to be unhappy?

00:18:28.810 --> 00:18:30.930
All right, be unhappy.

00:18:30.930 --> 00:18:37.600
You find people coming out of congregations,
which are supposed to be very religious so

00:18:37.600 --> 00:18:39.110
miserable looking.

00:18:39.110 --> 00:18:40.380
How can it be?

00:18:40.380 --> 00:18:46.600
It has to be joy, it has to be happiness.

00:18:46.600 --> 00:18:52.940
Just think of it, how can we ever believe
such things what we have believed for ages,

00:18:52.940 --> 00:18:59.300
ages, ages, and it can not go out of our heads,
that we have to suffer.

00:18:59.300 --> 00:19:04.120
How long, how many years, how many lives?

00:19:04.120 --> 00:19:06.120
Nothing is written anywhere.

00:19:06.120 --> 00:19:12.140
You better go on suffering and make others
suffer also with it.

00:19:12.140 --> 00:19:17.610
If some person is like that in your family
you’d like to run away with that boredom,

00:19:17.610 --> 00:19:20.460
because he’s suffering for nothing at all
and (Shri Mataji laughs) he don’t understand

00:19:20.460 --> 00:19:21.660
why is he suffering.

00:19:21.660 --> 00:19:24.520
So you want to run away from such a person.

00:19:24.520 --> 00:19:30.970
And all this kind of ideas we have accepted
for ages now.

00:19:30.970 --> 00:19:34.550
And that has led us to a big confusion about
God.

00:19:34.550 --> 00:19:38.970
Then we take to things which give us joy.

00:19:38.970 --> 00:19:44.650
Actually they are not, they are just flippant
pleasures.

00:19:44.650 --> 00:19:47.661
We can not enjoy anything in life, really
we can not.

00:19:47.661 --> 00:19:52.020
We can see the way people are now going on
for such sensational things.

00:19:52.020 --> 00:19:54.100
The reason is there’s no joy.

00:19:54.100 --> 00:20:00.930
The sensitivity to joy is so reduced that
I sometimes fear with all that they are doing

00:20:00.930 --> 00:20:06.090
they so fed up, that they may have to put
electrodes in the limbic area to get the joy

00:20:06.090 --> 00:20:08.600
instead.

00:20:08.600 --> 00:20:17.620
They have become so very (Shri Mataji smiles)
so very insensitive to anything, they’ll

00:20:17.620 --> 00:20:25.530
not laugh, they’ll not smile, they are so
full of closed hearts and frightened things,

00:20:25.530 --> 00:20:28.160
whatever they said about humane beings.

00:20:28.160 --> 00:20:39.090
Now first thing you have to know – you don’t
have to suffer at all.

00:20:39.090 --> 00:20:40.580
Secondly, you don’t have to judge yourself.

00:20:40.580 --> 00:20:42.690
Let your Kundalini rise and judge you.

00:20:42.690 --> 00:20:44.150
You don’t start judging yourself and condemning
yourself.

00:20:44.150 --> 00:20:50.320
And the another fashion, which is very common,
is to feel guilty.

00:20:50.320 --> 00:20:54.930
From the very beginning you start, “I am
afraid”.

00:20:54.930 --> 00:20:57.980
What are you afraid of?

00:20:57.980 --> 00:21:05.200
You have to have all the courage, all the
blessings, and all the confidence.

00:21:05.200 --> 00:21:11.880
You are a humane being and this is the message
I want to tell you that you are a humane being

00:21:11.880 --> 00:21:13.980
and you have to be the Spirit.

00:21:13.980 --> 00:21:18.670
And once you are the Spirit you’ll be surprised
the blessings will be showering upon you.

00:21:18.670 --> 00:21:22.610
In these modern times should talk about these
things is out of date.

00:21:22.610 --> 00:21:26.990
But it is predicted that this will be said
and this will be done.

00:21:26.990 --> 00:21:35.780
For us it is important first of all to know
our own glory, our own truths, and about how

00:21:35.780 --> 00:21:39.190
we are built and how others are built.

00:21:39.190 --> 00:21:45.020
Once you know that first of all the peace
within is established.

00:21:45.020 --> 00:21:51.160
Unless and until there is peace within what
do you talk of this peace organization and

00:21:51.160 --> 00:21:53.050
Peace Nobel Prize?

00:21:53.050 --> 00:22:02.750
I’ve seen the people who have gotten Nobel
Prizes are the most hot-headed so much that

00:22:02.750 --> 00:22:07.200
you have to talk to them with a barge pole
in between.

00:22:07.200 --> 00:22:12.480
Any time they are up to jump on you, you can
not challenge them; even talking to them is

00:22:12.480 --> 00:22:14.750
a difficult situation.

00:22:14.750 --> 00:22:21.370
So how are they going to have this peace foundation
when they are themselves so shaking?

00:22:21.370 --> 00:22:26.830
Then you have other things talking about – the
love, the love.

00:22:26.830 --> 00:22:30.050
Full of lust and greed.

00:22:30.050 --> 00:22:34.670
They love your purse, not you.

00:22:34.670 --> 00:22:41.500
When you talk of love, love is a thing that’s
detached.

00:22:41.500 --> 00:22:48.990
Like the sap in the tree rises, goes to all
the leaves, all the trunk, all the flowers,

00:22:48.990 --> 00:22:51.670
all the fruits and comes back, is not attached.

00:22:51.670 --> 00:23:00.250
If it’s get attached to one fruit the tree
will die and the fruit will die too.

00:23:00.250 --> 00:23:07.430
So this Pure Love or the Divine Love is detached,
that’s why it acts, it works.

00:23:07.430 --> 00:23:16.550
A person who is a Realized soul is such a
pure personality that even a glance of such

00:23:16.550 --> 00:23:20.250
a person can do lots of things.

00:23:20.250 --> 00:23:28.390
Even a thought of such a person in the attention
can do so many things, bring about so many

00:23:28.390 --> 00:23:29.390
changes.

00:23:29.390 --> 00:23:32.600
So this is the time of our transformation.

00:23:32.600 --> 00:23:41.230
We have to become a higher personality; the
transformation has to take place.

00:23:41.230 --> 00:23:46.870
At the time of Easter we give people eggs.

00:23:46.870 --> 00:23:52.070
Perhaps people do not know why do we give
them eggs at the time of Easter.

00:23:52.070 --> 00:23:57.590
But about Christ is written in our Scriptures
that He was an egg to begin with.

00:23:57.590 --> 00:24:04.480
Of course, He was much more before that, but
to begin with He was the God of innocence.

00:24:04.480 --> 00:24:09.200
But then He came as an egg.

00:24:09.200 --> 00:24:12.080
And then He was divided into two halves.

00:24:12.080 --> 00:24:19.920
The one half, which incarnated, and which
transformed this Earth.

00:24:19.920 --> 00:24:23.240
So the resurrection is the transformation.

00:24:23.240 --> 00:24:32.770
Like an egg, if we are bound by our conditioning
and by our ego, we break through that shell

00:24:32.770 --> 00:24:35.820
and become a bird, which is really a free
bird.

00:24:35.820 --> 00:24:39.060
Only thing, the bird has to know how to fly.

00:24:39.060 --> 00:24:47.140
Now this is, again I’m saying is the living
process of the living nature, of the living

00:24:47.140 --> 00:24:48.520
Power of Love.

00:24:48.520 --> 00:24:51.020
It is not something artificial.

00:24:51.020 --> 00:24:58.780
In Sahaja Yoga, I must have spoken in this
hall I don’t know how many times might before

00:24:58.780 --> 00:25:02.830
and again today there’s a chance to speak
to you.

00:25:02.830 --> 00:25:08.020
What I have to say, that it is important the
becoming.

00:25:08.020 --> 00:25:14.230
Is not important: you can not become a member
of Sahaj Yog, you can not pay membership,

00:25:14.230 --> 00:25:15.870
you can not pay for your Realization.

00:25:15.870 --> 00:25:16.880
How can you pay?

00:25:16.880 --> 00:25:23.300
How much do we pay to the Mother Earth to
sprout the seed, does She understand?

00:25:23.300 --> 00:25:28.650
Because She has the power She sprouts the
seed.

00:25:28.650 --> 00:25:36.330
If you give Her money or read something before
Her, it makes no difference.

00:25:36.330 --> 00:25:41.740
But once you get your Realization you start
understanding how many powers you have.

00:25:41.740 --> 00:25:48.930
And the greatest power is of compassion and
detached love.

00:25:48.930 --> 00:25:53.740
These seven chakras are within us, which are
to be enlightened by the awakening of the

00:25:53.740 --> 00:25:57.220
Kundalini about which Dr. Spiro has already
told you.

00:25:57.220 --> 00:26:01.830
Now in this short time I can not cover up
the whole subject.

00:26:01.830 --> 00:26:06.400
I must have given at least more than thousand
lectures in English language.

00:26:06.400 --> 00:26:14.270
But I would request you one thing that forget
about what you have learned so far.

00:26:14.270 --> 00:26:22.120
About your conditionings because if you had
achieved anything out of that I was not necessary.

00:26:22.120 --> 00:26:31.200
Now you have to see with a clean slate, as
they say, what you can achieve in this lifetime,

00:26:31.200 --> 00:26:35.070
which is the most important thing, is to be
achieved.

00:26:35.070 --> 00:26:44.440
Of course, where’s a lot of things that
should really make you more tempting about

00:26:44.440 --> 00:26:45.490
it.

00:26:45.490 --> 00:26:49.000
Firstly, that you get rid of all your illnesses.

00:26:49.000 --> 00:26:57.110
Most of the illnesses can be cured – if
they are at an early stage – by Sahaja Yoga.

00:26:57.110 --> 00:27:03.360
Most of the mental illnesses can be cured
with Sahaja Yoga.

00:27:03.360 --> 00:27:08.420
Your material problems can be solved by Sahaja
Yoga.

00:27:08.420 --> 00:27:13.530
Your spiritual problems like going to wrong
gurus and wrong people whatever you have accumulated

00:27:13.530 --> 00:27:15.480
within you can be corrected.

00:27:15.480 --> 00:27:22.710
But the highest of all that you become sensitive
to joy.

00:27:22.710 --> 00:27:25.320
Then you start seeing joy in everything.

00:27:25.320 --> 00:27:29.800
You don’t have to think that, “Oh, this
is the thing which is marvelous”.

00:27:29.800 --> 00:27:30.800
No.

00:27:30.800 --> 00:27:34.720
It just happens, you see it is.

00:27:34.720 --> 00:27:39.370
Just you enjoy without thinking about it.

00:27:39.370 --> 00:27:41.380
You become a peaceful personality.

00:27:41.380 --> 00:27:43.800
You become a dynamic personality.

00:27:43.800 --> 00:27:50.450
Your are not spade by other veils of things,
like some fashion coming up, then some sort

00:27:50.450 --> 00:27:55.910
of a nonsensical idea coming up, then some
medicine coming up and you treating yourself

00:27:55.910 --> 00:27:57.780
and getting to trouble.

00:27:57.780 --> 00:28:02.080
You just rise above all the these things at
a higher level and you start see everything

00:28:02.080 --> 00:28:04.070
as a witness.

00:28:04.070 --> 00:28:10.350
You become the witness of all the jokes that
are going on and you just watch it and you

00:28:10.350 --> 00:28:13.030
think, “What’s all this?

00:28:13.030 --> 00:28:15.820
Is just a play”.

00:28:15.820 --> 00:28:20.550
Many people have said that, “Mother, You
always laugh so much and You have always smiling

00:28:20.550 --> 00:28:23.380
face, so the people are not going to take
You seriously”.

00:28:23.380 --> 00:28:26.690
I said, “I don’t want them to be serious”.

00:28:26.690 --> 00:28:28.070
There’s not going to be any seriousness
needed.

00:28:28.070 --> 00:28:30.900
What are you serious about?

00:28:30.900 --> 00:28:33.210
You should be happy.

00:28:33.210 --> 00:28:34.300
It’s fun.

00:28:34.300 --> 00:28:36.510
We have to be happy people.

00:28:36.510 --> 00:28:37.520
We have to be happy.

00:28:37.520 --> 00:28:43.580
Most people who think, they are very guilty,
should punish themselves by saying, “You

00:28:43.580 --> 00:28:45.990
are not guilty, you are not guilty” 108
times.

00:28:45.990 --> 00:28:49.040
That’s what we have in Sahaja Yoga.

00:28:49.040 --> 00:28:50.040
Is just the myth.

00:28:50.040 --> 00:28:55.760
All these are myths; we are working with myths
and making our lives miserable, which is meant

00:28:55.760 --> 00:29:03.440
to be joy, happiness and all the overflowing
blessings of the Divine.

00:29:03.440 --> 00:29:11.550
Whatever I’m telling you about we have within
ourselves all the great powers hidden of our

00:29:11.550 --> 00:29:18.120
brain, of our liver, of our heart, – they
are to be enlightened.

00:29:18.120 --> 00:29:19.160
And then in the light you see everything.

00:29:19.160 --> 00:29:25.910
But as in this room you have so many lights
you have to just push in one button and the

00:29:25.910 --> 00:29:26.960
whole thing comes out.

00:29:26.960 --> 00:29:28.640
In the same way it happens.

00:29:28.640 --> 00:29:34.070
But if I start telling you about the history
of electricity in the dark and all about how

00:29:34.070 --> 00:29:39.470
it came here and what all happened, you’d
be just fed up with it.

00:29:39.470 --> 00:29:44.970
So what we are doing is to tell you that let
us put on the button first, you better have

00:29:44.970 --> 00:29:49.250
your light and see in that light if it is
true or not.

00:29:49.250 --> 00:29:54.840
If it is true you have to understand and accept
it honestly.

00:29:54.840 --> 00:29:59.960
You have to be honest to yourself that is
the main point I’m trying to tell you.

00:29:59.960 --> 00:30:04.270
We are not to play about with ourselves and
play about with our conditionings.

00:30:04.270 --> 00:30:09.660
We have to be honest and to get to our properties
that are within our selves.

00:30:09.660 --> 00:30:13.060
I’m not here to oblige you at all, there’s
no obligation.

00:30:13.060 --> 00:30:18.720
Is just like a catalyst, I would say, and
you become the catalyst oneself once you get

00:30:18.720 --> 00:30:19.830
your Realization.

00:30:19.830 --> 00:30:26.070
And you can do all that I can do, it’s very
easy and very simple.

00:30:26.070 --> 00:30:30.180
May God bless you all.

00:30:30.180 --> 00:30:31.180
(Aside) Now, should we have questions or what?

00:30:31.180 --> 00:30:32.180
I find most of you were just ready for getting
Self-Realization.

00:30:32.180 --> 00:30:34.750
Not only that, but I think you all capable
of that.

00:30:34.750 --> 00:31:22.730
