be want to ask questions.

00:31:22.730 --> 00:31:27.290
I would only request – don’t be aggressive
with Me, there’s no need.

00:31:27.290 --> 00:31:33.660
I’ve not come here for votes, nor for any
money, nor for anything.

00:31:33.660 --> 00:31:38.480
I’ve just come here to give you your own
keys.

00:31:38.480 --> 00:31:41.830
Out of Love that I am.

00:31:41.830 --> 00:31:45.610
So please try to understand Me.

00:31:45.610 --> 00:31:50.630
I’m not here to take, I mean, anything from
you.

00:31:50.630 --> 00:31:57.760
Just to show you what you are and you’ll
be happy to know that you are something great.

00:31:57.760 --> 00:32:05.610
So may God bless you, I would like you to
ask Me questions related to Self-Realization

00:32:05.610 --> 00:32:10.700
and not to waste the time of so many who look
so anxious to have their Self-Realization.

00:32:10.700 --> 00:32:18.740
Those who do not want to do any meditation
after this, which will take hardly ten minutes

00:32:18.740 --> 00:32:23.559
for you to get your Realization, because the
journey is three to four feet only – from

00:32:23.559 --> 00:32:24.559
here to here.

00:32:24.559 --> 00:32:27.880
(Shri Mataji shows the distance from Mooladhar
to Sahasrara Chakra with Her hand.)

00:32:27.880 --> 00:32:28.880
That’s all.

00:32:28.880 --> 00:32:33.420
So, I would just say, that you will all get
your Realization in no time.

00:32:33.420 --> 00:32:38.840
Should get your Realization, but do not try
to be uncivil.

00:32:38.840 --> 00:32:43.490
If you do not want to have it, you should
leave the hall and leave others in peace.

00:32:43.490 --> 00:32:45.610
That would be very kind of us.

00:32:45.610 --> 00:32:50.380
And not to see and watch, we don’t need
such people here.

00:32:50.380 --> 00:32:55.980
Those who want to have Realization can sit
down or others have freedom to go, but not

00:32:55.980 --> 00:32:57.120
freedom to sit here.

00:32:57.120 --> 00:33:06.910
So I would request you to be kind and civil
to others who want to receive their Realization.

