Could You say something to finish of what
he said?

00:33:54.390 --> 00:33:56.309
Shri Mataji: Generating principle?

00:33:56.309 --> 00:33:57.380
The Sahaja Yogi: Germinating.

00:33:57.380 --> 00:34:00.130
Shri Mataji: You see, it is, I would say,
it is spontaneous.

00:34:00.130 --> 00:34:11.560
Now that should explain a little bit how does
a seed germinate.

00:34:11.560 --> 00:34:15.960
You have the seed and you put it in the Mother
Earth, all right?

00:34:15.960 --> 00:34:22.490
And it germinates because it’s all built
in it, this is all built in it, all this is

00:34:22.490 --> 00:34:23.649
built in it.

00:34:23.649 --> 00:34:30.220
And in the triangular bone you have got this
Kundalini, which is placed within you in 3,5

00:34:30.220 --> 00:34:32.740
coils of an energy, which is a residual energy.

00:34:32.740 --> 00:34:41.890
Which is actually the power of your pure desire.

00:34:41.890 --> 00:34:46.710
Because the desire that we have otherwise,
all the desires, are not pure.

00:34:46.710 --> 00:34:50.510
What’s why they are not satiable in general.

00:34:50.510 --> 00:34:52.720
We get one thing, we want to have another.

00:34:52.720 --> 00:34:55.659
We get the another thing, you want to have
the third thing.

00:34:55.659 --> 00:35:01.079
So this is the power of pure desire.

00:35:01.079 --> 00:35:10.369
And this pure desire is described in the Bible
as Holy Ghost, in the Koran as [SOUNDS LIKE

00:35:10.369 --> 00:35:19.680
– Asas] and in the Indian Scriptures as
Adi Shakti, as the Primordial Mother.

00:35:19.680 --> 00:35:25.880
So She is the power of God as called as the
Primordial Mother.

00:35:25.880 --> 00:35:33.869
Now this Primordial Mother is settled in our
triangular bone while the Spirit which is

00:35:33.869 --> 00:35:37.640
the reflection of God Almighty is in our heart.

00:35:37.640 --> 00:35:47.100
But the seat of the heart is on top of your
head – here – on the fontanel bone area,

00:35:47.100 --> 00:35:50.660
which is called as Brahmarandra in Sanskrit
language.

00:35:50.660 --> 00:35:57.740
And also when we talk of baptism we try to
bless there, but it’s artificial.

00:35:57.740 --> 00:36:06.130
Real baptism is when this Kundalini, which
is the Holy Ghost or the Adi Shakti, the reflection

00:36:06.130 --> 00:36:13.320
of that, rises within you piercing through
these centers, piercing through the fontanel

00:36:13.320 --> 00:36:22.000
bone area and actualizes the experience of
this personal experience and gives you a cool

00:36:22.000 --> 00:36:23.990
breeze coming out of your head.

00:36:23.990 --> 00:36:28.130
Actually the cool breeze coming out of your
head, you feel it, and then you feel it everywhere,

00:36:28.130 --> 00:36:32.140
the cool breeze of the Holy Ghost.

00:36:32.140 --> 00:36:40.020
And that is the subtle of the subtlest, which
is the syntheses of all the powers, which

00:36:40.020 --> 00:36:42.470
works everything out.

00:36:42.470 --> 00:36:49.710
Like you can say, in the sulfur dioxide we
have in the molecule of the sulfur dioxide

00:36:49.710 --> 00:36:52.230
we find that there is pulsation of the vibrations.

00:36:52.230 --> 00:36:54.840
Who does what?

00:36:54.840 --> 00:36:56.900
We say electromagnetic.

00:36:56.900 --> 00:37:01.350
But the electromagnetic is one part of the
same power.

00:37:01.350 --> 00:37:05.300
So this power we can broadly divide into three
things.

00:37:05.300 --> 00:37:11.160
In the first power what we call as the power
by which we desire.

00:37:11.160 --> 00:37:19.650
The second power by which we act and the third
power by which we ascend.

00:37:19.650 --> 00:37:31.070
All the synthesis of all these powers, all
these powers are in this Kundalini which meets

00:37:31.070 --> 00:37:37.030
the Spirit because the seat of the Spirit,
as they call the Pitha, is on top of your

00:37:37.030 --> 00:37:42.600
head and that’s how the whole attention
you can see like a sari it is supposing the

00:37:42.600 --> 00:37:47.359
attention is spread here and the Kundalini
rises, rises like that (Shri Mataji puts Her

00:37:47.359 --> 00:37:49.131
finger under the sari on Her chest and erects
it like a tent pole), pierces through this

00:37:49.131 --> 00:37:51.930
at and the whole of this attention becomes
enlightened.

00:37:51.930 --> 00:37:55.450
That’s how your attention becomes enlightened.

00:37:55.450 --> 00:37:57.200
This is in short I’m telling you.

00:37:57.200 --> 00:38:03.900
But as I told you we have got My lectures
on all detailed way how it works out, it’s

00:38:03.900 --> 00:38:05.160
quite a detailed thing.

00:38:05.160 --> 00:38:08.290
But in the first lecture it will be quite
boring for you.

00:38:08.290 --> 00:38:13.490
So I think I better tell you this much, that
it’s a spontaneous happening and can happen

00:38:13.490 --> 00:38:36.590
to all of you.

