of the Holy Ghost?

01:07:57.110 --> 01:07:59.230
Mother, is this the Brahma Shakti?

01:07:59.230 --> 01:08:06.880
Mother, is this the All Pervading Power of
God’s Love?”

01:08:06.880 --> 01:08:12.800
Just ask the question.

01:08:12.800 --> 01:08:17.440
Now put down your hands.

