01:09:02.859 --> 01:09:12.849
Both hands to be raised those who are feeling
it.

01:09:12.849 --> 01:09:18.309
Just imagine!

01:09:18.309 --> 01:09:21.390
Most of them have felt it.

01:09:21.390 --> 01:09:22.609
Imagine.

01:09:22.609 --> 01:09:25.060
Hardly very few haven’t felt.

01:09:25.060 --> 01:09:33.579
It’s very easy for them also to feel it
and if they want they can come up to the stage

01:09:33.579 --> 01:09:35.519
